dct_title_s: Map of routes fromo San Joaquin Valley Road to Yosemite Valley
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; E.J.B.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper left.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Table of Distances, with inset location map of California.
Numbered 130 in lower left and 55 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
